WEBVTT

00:01:40.180 --> 00:01:44.800
=Love Story in the 1970s=

00:01:45.100 --> 00:01:47.940
=Episode 11=

00:01:50.648 --> 00:01:52.110
You two are not sleeping together?

00:01:53.940 --> 00:01:54.980
Of course we are.

00:01:56.250 --> 00:01:57.580
Then, what's with the bunk bed?

00:01:57.580 --> 00:01:59.010
We sleep on the bottom,

00:01:59.010 --> 00:02:00.420
and use the top for storage.

00:02:00.420 --> 00:02:01.170
It's practical.

00:02:01.600 --> 00:02:02.980
- Storage?
- Yeah, storage.

00:02:03.426 --> 00:02:04.460
There's a lot of stuff.

00:02:04.510 --> 00:02:05.340
See?

00:02:09.340 --> 00:02:10.740
Well, that's new.

00:02:12.530 --> 00:02:13.780
Honestly,

00:02:13.850 --> 00:02:15.020
regular beds are expensive.

00:02:15.020 --> 00:02:16.180
We can't afford one.

00:02:16.250 --> 00:02:17.860
So we went with this.

00:02:17.860 --> 00:02:19.570
No one wanted it, so we grabbed it.

00:02:20.740 --> 00:02:21.620
It's nice. Really.

00:02:21.850 --> 00:02:23.900
Well, we're neighbors now,

00:02:23.900 --> 00:02:24.760
so we'll be

00:02:24.760 --> 00:02:25.690
seeing each other.

00:02:25.940 --> 00:02:26.850
I won't keep you.

00:02:26.850 --> 00:02:27.530
I'll get going.

00:02:27.530 --> 00:02:28.590
- I'll walk you out.
- No need.

00:02:28.604 --> 00:02:29.620
You stay. I'll head off.

00:02:29.940 --> 00:02:30.900
- Alright.
- Bye.

00:02:37.460 --> 00:02:38.620
That was close.

00:02:38.620 --> 00:02:39.570
Way too close.

00:02:40.690 --> 00:02:41.950
She kind of had a point, though.

00:02:42.340 --> 00:02:43.530
Maybe we could squeeze in

00:02:43.530 --> 00:02:44.671
and use the top for storage.

00:02:44.680 --> 00:02:46.530
In your dreams. Get cleaning.

00:02:49.180 --> 00:02:51.500
(Jiangnan Municipal People's Hospital)

00:02:51.500 --> 00:02:53.760
(Doctors' Office)

00:02:53.760 --> 00:02:54.410
Qu,

00:02:54.880 --> 00:02:56.790
let's grab some lunch.

00:02:57.650 --> 00:02:58.650
I'll pass. You go ahead.

00:03:00.220 --> 00:03:01.690
Your wife brings you meals anyway.

00:03:02.940 --> 00:03:03.740
All right.

00:03:04.020 --> 00:03:05.810
I'll head out first, then.

00:03:08.620 --> 00:03:09.460
Dr. Qu,

00:03:10.340 --> 00:03:11.180
your lunch.

00:03:12.570 --> 00:03:13.460
Where's Fang Mujing?

00:03:14.300 --> 00:03:14.920
Ms. Fang?

00:03:14.920 --> 00:03:15.940
She's at school.

00:03:15.940 --> 00:03:17.500
She said from now on, I'll bring

00:03:17.500 --> 00:03:18.430
your meals and clothes.

00:03:21.460 --> 00:03:22.960
All right. I'll get going.

00:03:46.500 --> 00:03:47.280
You're back.

00:03:52.471 --> 00:03:53.937
Why didn't you go to the hospital?

00:03:56.620 --> 00:03:57.460
I did for a week

00:03:57.810 --> 00:03:59.550
to fulfill my duties as a wife.

00:04:00.340 --> 00:04:01.020
I'm done.

00:04:01.440 --> 00:04:02.900
I have my own work.

00:04:04.900 --> 00:04:06.120
You just wanted to prove

00:04:06.715 --> 00:04:08.226
you're prettier than the others.

00:04:09.300 --> 00:04:10.990
I want to prove a math theorem.

00:05:06.370 --> 00:05:07.690
You don't love me at all.

00:05:08.890 --> 00:05:10.060
Do you love me?

00:05:14.060 --> 00:05:15.300
Is it that you can't answer

00:05:16.210 --> 00:05:17.570
or you won't?

00:05:19.450 --> 00:05:20.810
I just won't tell a lie

00:05:21.420 --> 00:05:23.130
that's exposed
the moment it's questioned.

00:05:26.026 --> 00:05:27.660
You won't lower yourself to love me.

00:05:27.660 --> 00:05:28.450
I understand.

00:05:29.010 --> 00:05:31.010
But don't expect me
to fawn over you either.

00:05:31.540 --> 00:05:32.770
I hope you understand that.

00:05:34.220 --> 00:05:35.190
Love takes time for me.

00:05:35.190 --> 00:05:36.060
For me too.

00:05:39.300 --> 00:05:40.450
If there's nothing else,

00:05:41.370 --> 00:05:43.300
I'd like to finish writing that proof.

00:06:25.980 --> 00:06:28.140
(Jiangcheng)

00:06:34.620 --> 00:06:35.060
Ni.

00:06:35.540 --> 00:06:36.100
Hey, Brother.

00:06:36.182 --> 00:06:36.940
Thanks for coming.

00:06:36.960 --> 00:06:38.010
- It's nothing.
- I've got it.

00:06:38.010 --> 00:06:38.540
Fang Muyang,

00:06:38.740 --> 00:06:40.370
take my luggage home first.

00:06:40.660 --> 00:06:42.100
I need to run an errand.

00:06:42.740 --> 00:06:43.500
What errand?

00:06:45.300 --> 00:06:46.250
I'm going to Lin Mei's.

00:06:48.770 --> 00:06:50.370
You really are her brother.

00:06:50.760 --> 00:06:52.010
I was thinking the same thing.

00:06:52.060 --> 00:06:53.570
I was thinking we'd go to Lin Mei's

00:06:53.570 --> 00:06:55.180
and propose when you've arrived.

00:06:55.500 --> 00:06:56.500
That won't do.

00:06:56.690 --> 00:06:58.370
I can't let you tag along to a proposal.

00:06:59.060 --> 00:07:00.100
Why not?

00:07:00.100 --> 00:07:02.300
You know what her parents are like.

00:07:02.300 --> 00:07:03.890
If Mom and Dad go, it'll end in a fight.

00:07:03.890 --> 00:07:05.180
I'm the perfect choice.

00:07:05.180 --> 00:07:06.130
I'm a girl,

00:07:06.130 --> 00:07:07.620
and I'm Lin Mei's best friend.

00:07:07.660 --> 00:07:10.100
They won't say anything harsh to me.

00:07:10.100 --> 00:07:11.570
I've talked it through with Lin Mei.

00:07:11.570 --> 00:07:12.450
Let's go.

00:07:13.540 --> 00:07:14.130
Wait.

00:07:15.570 --> 00:07:16.210
Bring these.

00:07:16.210 --> 00:07:17.420
I picked these for her parents.

00:07:17.420 --> 00:07:17.810
Come on.

00:07:18.210 --> 00:07:19.370
Let Mom and Dad know.

00:07:20.690 --> 00:07:21.210
Brother.

00:07:21.740 --> 00:07:22.660
Go get her.

00:07:23.690 --> 00:07:25.370
Smart move buying these.

00:07:25.570 --> 00:07:26.060
It's mine!

00:07:27.300 --> 00:07:30.100
Easy. Why are you pressing so hard?

00:07:30.100 --> 00:07:30.950
I'm taking your piece.

00:07:32.540 --> 00:07:33.740
When you play on my board,

00:07:33.740 --> 00:07:34.890
you press harder than that.

00:07:34.890 --> 00:07:36.250
Your board? What board is that?

00:07:36.250 --> 00:07:37.450
Can it compare to mine?

00:07:37.450 --> 00:07:39.660
This is a sandalwood chessboard.

00:07:39.737 --> 00:07:40.620
Sandalwood, you know?

00:07:40.740 --> 00:07:42.180
It just sounds premium.

00:07:43.810 --> 00:07:44.890
Fine, I'll be gentler.

00:07:47.010 --> 00:07:47.500
Fei,

00:07:48.060 --> 00:07:49.770
before the others get here,

00:07:49.810 --> 00:07:50.860
let me ask you something.

00:07:52.420 --> 00:07:54.130
When Fei Ni got married,

00:07:54.450 --> 00:07:55.940
why wasn't there a wedding?

00:07:56.660 --> 00:07:58.690
If she'd married Ye Feng,

00:07:59.690 --> 00:08:01.570
there would've been a banquet, right?

00:08:02.271 --> 00:08:03.980
Liu, that's the problem with you.

00:08:03.980 --> 00:08:05.093
You're too materialistic.

00:08:05.450 --> 00:08:07.370
What matters most in a marriage?

00:08:07.420 --> 00:08:09.060
The person you're marrying.

00:08:09.450 --> 00:08:11.450
Can Ye Feng compare to Fang?

00:08:11.450 --> 00:08:13.370
Fang is a hero.

00:08:14.210 --> 00:08:15.570
No offense,

00:08:16.570 --> 00:08:18.370
but you're muddleheaded at chess,

00:08:18.370 --> 00:08:20.426
and just as muddleheaded
picking a son-in-law.

00:08:21.180 --> 00:08:22.660
A title?

00:08:23.010 --> 00:08:24.570
What does that really prove?

00:08:28.620 --> 00:08:29.980
Has he dated anyone before?

00:08:31.330 --> 00:08:33.460
Did he get into trouble
in the countryside?

00:08:35.210 --> 00:08:36.610
Does he have a child?

00:08:37.450 --> 00:08:38.690
Do you know any of that?

00:08:44.940 --> 00:08:46.300
Of course I do.

00:08:47.450 --> 00:08:48.970
He was recognized by both

00:08:48.970 --> 00:08:51.900
the Educated Youth Office
and the factory administration.

00:08:52.060 --> 00:08:54.260
Wouldn't they know his background?

00:08:54.970 --> 00:08:57.690
The Educated Youth Office
won't be the one marrying him.

00:09:02.730 --> 00:09:03.610
Checkmate.

00:09:06.850 --> 00:09:07.450
I'm done.

00:09:07.450 --> 00:09:10.180
Come on, there are still moves left.

00:09:12.090 --> 00:09:14.490
No more chess today
because your son comes home?

00:09:15.660 --> 00:09:16.180
Honey.

00:09:16.780 --> 00:09:17.330
Honey.

00:09:17.690 --> 00:09:18.180
What is it?

00:09:18.180 --> 00:09:20.182
When I was playing chess
with Liu just now,

00:09:20.360 --> 00:09:21.900
he said something

00:09:22.080 --> 00:09:22.970
that got me thinking.

00:09:23.300 --> 00:09:25.050
Why do we trust Fang Muyang

00:09:25.050 --> 00:09:26.610
so wholeheartedly?

00:09:27.060 --> 00:09:28.380
What's not to trust?

00:09:28.420 --> 00:09:29.780
I think he's a good kid.

00:09:29.810 --> 00:09:30.300
He is.

00:09:30.640 --> 00:09:32.260
He does seem decent.

00:09:32.490 --> 00:09:34.310
But I can't help worrying.

00:09:34.690 --> 00:09:35.790
What if Fang Muyang

00:09:35.790 --> 00:09:37.900
is hiding something from us?

00:09:38.480 --> 00:09:40.900
He and Ni were classmates
in middle school,

00:09:40.900 --> 00:09:42.900
but they hadn't seen
each other for seven years.

00:09:43.020 --> 00:09:45.060
While he was
at the educated youth post,

00:09:45.060 --> 00:09:46.540
did he date anyone?

00:09:47.380 --> 00:09:48.970
Did he get into any trouble?

00:09:48.970 --> 00:09:50.450
We don't know.

00:09:51.982 --> 00:09:53.490
You're only thinking of this now?

00:09:53.690 --> 00:09:55.260
They've already registered.

00:09:55.290 --> 00:09:56.720
What's the point of second-guessing?

00:09:56.760 --> 00:09:59.204
Run all the way
to Great Northern Wilderness over this?

00:09:59.420 --> 00:10:00.582
I wouldn't go that far.

00:10:02.850 --> 00:10:04.300
Still,

00:10:04.970 --> 00:10:08.020
it's better to find out
than stay in the dark.

00:10:08.450 --> 00:10:09.300
Besides,

00:10:09.300 --> 00:10:11.420
what if something did happen?

00:10:15.420 --> 00:10:16.420
So what's your plan?

00:10:18.850 --> 00:10:20.570
I've got an idea.

00:10:20.900 --> 00:10:21.850
Hear me out.

00:10:23.720 --> 00:10:24.820
They say

00:10:25.071 --> 00:10:26.780
the truth comes out after a few drinks.

00:10:27.020 --> 00:10:28.900
Tonight, I'll bring some liquor

00:10:28.900 --> 00:10:30.970
and get Comrade Fang drunk.

00:10:30.970 --> 00:10:32.900
We'll see what he really has to say.

00:10:33.380 --> 00:10:35.450
When you men get drunk,
it's all nonsense.

00:10:35.450 --> 00:10:36.810
There's no "truth."

00:10:37.690 --> 00:10:41.020
If two out of ten
drunken ramblings are real, it's enough.

00:10:43.450 --> 00:10:45.260
Fine. Go ahead.

00:10:47.420 --> 00:10:48.850
We're out of liquor at home.

00:10:49.060 --> 00:10:50.260
Apply for a liquor coupon.

00:10:51.090 --> 00:10:53.180
So all that talk was
just an excuse to drink?

00:10:54.060 --> 00:10:55.020
No, no!

00:10:55.020 --> 00:10:57.450
You know

00:10:57.450 --> 00:10:59.450
I haven't been feeling well lately.

00:10:59.810 --> 00:11:01.260
The smell of alcohol makes me sick.

00:11:01.260 --> 00:11:02.260
I can barely stand it.

00:11:02.260 --> 00:11:03.690
I'm doing this for our daughter.

00:11:03.690 --> 00:11:05.180
I'm making a sacrifice here.

00:11:06.804 --> 00:11:07.690
How much do you need?

00:11:09.210 --> 00:11:11.420
The kid can't hold his liquor.

00:11:11.420 --> 00:11:12.690
100 to 150 mL at most.

00:11:13.140 --> 00:11:14.090
So, I'll get 500 mL.

00:11:14.450 --> 00:11:15.260
How much?

00:11:15.450 --> 00:11:16.260
500 mL liquor.

00:11:16.300 --> 00:11:16.900
500 mL?

00:11:16.900 --> 00:11:17.780
No, no...

00:11:17.780 --> 00:11:19.610
Better safe than sorry.

00:11:19.610 --> 00:11:20.810
What if he doesn't get drunk

00:11:20.810 --> 00:11:22.260
and nothing comes out?

00:11:22.260 --> 00:11:23.380
It'll all be for nothing.

00:11:23.850 --> 00:11:25.680
You can't catch a wolf without bait.

00:11:28.900 --> 00:11:29.350
Fine.

00:11:36.260 --> 00:11:39.420
I've heard of brothers
proposing for their sisters,

00:11:39.420 --> 00:11:41.330
but a sister proposing for her brother?

00:11:41.330 --> 00:11:42.850
That's a first for me.

00:11:43.490 --> 00:11:45.970
Mrs. Lin, I'm always
at your place anyway.

00:11:45.970 --> 00:11:46.970
I know it well.

00:11:47.190 --> 00:11:48.570
So I volunteered.

00:11:49.180 --> 00:11:51.410
Fei Ni, you're always welcome

00:11:51.410 --> 00:11:53.300
to visit us.

00:11:53.660 --> 00:11:56.090
But if you're here
to propose for your brother,

00:11:56.090 --> 00:11:58.690
don't expect me to smile about it.

00:11:58.690 --> 00:12:00.900
You know exactly what I'm like.

00:12:00.900 --> 00:12:03.180
I have a reputation for being picky.

00:12:03.570 --> 00:12:04.060
Mom,

00:12:04.500 --> 00:12:05.900
how can you say that?

00:12:05.900 --> 00:12:07.060
Because it's true.

00:12:07.210 --> 00:12:08.900
I like men with good education,

00:12:08.900 --> 00:12:11.260
steady jobs,
and preferably housing of their own.

00:12:12.020 --> 00:12:14.610
Fei Ting, which of those do you have?

00:12:14.610 --> 00:12:15.980
(Lin Mei's Father)

00:12:18.380 --> 00:12:19.490
He qualifies as "a man."

00:12:19.690 --> 00:12:21.180
And who isn't?

00:12:25.210 --> 00:12:26.570
Our Lin Mei

00:12:26.780 --> 00:12:28.490
may not be highly educated,

00:12:28.493 --> 00:12:30.660
but she works at
the Supply and Marketing Cooperative.

00:12:30.660 --> 00:12:31.970
The Cooperative!

00:12:32.020 --> 00:12:33.540
Do you know how many people

00:12:33.540 --> 00:12:34.900
can't even get in there?

00:12:35.380 --> 00:12:36.690
Look at all the things you bought.

00:12:36.690 --> 00:12:38.380
This pile of stuff

00:12:38.780 --> 00:12:41.570
was all purchased from the Cooperative.

00:12:41.570 --> 00:12:42.090
Right?

00:12:43.490 --> 00:12:46.090
Let me be honest with you.

00:12:46.300 --> 00:12:48.610
There's a young man from the bus station

00:12:48.610 --> 00:12:50.570
who's been pursuing our Lin Mei.

00:12:50.610 --> 00:12:52.970
He drives a passenger bus.

00:12:53.210 --> 00:12:54.660
You've heard the saying, right?

00:12:54.660 --> 00:12:56.210
Once you've got your hands on the wheel,

00:12:56.210 --> 00:12:58.020
you wouldn't trade it
for a county chief.

00:12:59.450 --> 00:13:01.900
Fei Ting,
where have you been assigned?

00:13:03.180 --> 00:13:05.090
Mrs. Lin, I just returned to the city.

00:13:05.260 --> 00:13:06.404
I haven't been assigned yet.

00:13:06.404 --> 00:13:08.160
So, is that no assignment yet,

00:13:08.160 --> 00:13:10.180
or no chance of getting one?

00:13:12.780 --> 00:13:14.970
Let me be clear today.

00:13:15.780 --> 00:13:17.420
You two are not a match.

00:13:17.420 --> 00:13:18.730
We don't approve.

00:13:18.730 --> 00:13:20.540
So give up on this idea.

00:13:20.540 --> 00:13:21.380
And take back

00:13:21.380 --> 00:13:22.330
all these gifts.

00:13:22.330 --> 00:13:24.420
You can use them
for your next blind date.

00:13:24.660 --> 00:13:25.420
Please, Mrs. Lin...

00:13:25.420 --> 00:13:25.940
Mom...

00:13:26.780 --> 00:13:28.610
Mrs. Lin, I don't think

00:13:29.020 --> 00:13:30.420
you're snobbish.

00:13:30.848 --> 00:13:32.210
I think you're just shortsighted.

00:13:33.310 --> 00:13:34.210
What do you mean?

00:13:34.730 --> 00:13:36.650
That young man from the bus station,

00:13:37.160 --> 00:13:38.420
his name is Chen Yunguo, right?

00:13:38.610 --> 00:13:39.150
That's right.

00:13:39.940 --> 00:13:41.010
To be honest,

00:13:41.490 --> 00:13:42.780
he wooed me too.

00:13:43.380 --> 00:13:44.730
So you see,

00:13:44.730 --> 00:13:45.870
aside from having a good job,

00:13:45.870 --> 00:13:46.690
he's slick-tongued,

00:13:46.970 --> 00:13:48.140
always on the road,

00:13:48.140 --> 00:13:49.610
traveling all over.

00:13:49.610 --> 00:13:50.940
Can you really be sure

00:13:50.940 --> 00:13:51.900
he'll settle down

00:13:51.900 --> 00:13:53.020
with Lin Mei?

00:13:56.090 --> 00:13:56.580
Yes,

00:13:56.940 --> 00:13:57.970
my brother

00:13:57.970 --> 00:13:59.970
hasn't secured a job yet.

00:14:00.090 --> 00:14:01.300
But he will.

00:14:01.570 --> 00:14:02.260
Look at him.

00:14:02.450 --> 00:14:03.060
He's steady,

00:14:03.200 --> 00:14:03.900
reliable,

00:14:04.010 --> 00:14:04.630
mature,

00:14:05.060 --> 00:14:06.140
responsible,

00:14:06.140 --> 00:14:07.140
and caring.

00:14:07.490 --> 00:14:09.900
Lin Mei would never suffer marrying him.

00:14:11.380 --> 00:14:12.490
And Mrs. Lin,

00:14:13.140 --> 00:14:14.420
everyone in our family,

00:14:14.420 --> 00:14:15.490
from top to bottom,

00:14:16.020 --> 00:14:17.140
adores Lin Mei.

00:14:17.330 --> 00:14:18.420
She'd be welcomed.

00:14:18.610 --> 00:14:21.020
We grew up together.

00:14:21.180 --> 00:14:22.690
If anyone ever dared bully her,

00:14:22.690 --> 00:14:24.970
I'd be the first to stand up for her.

00:14:29.330 --> 00:14:30.140
Yes.

00:14:31.330 --> 00:14:33.780
Our family isn't wealthy.

00:14:34.540 --> 00:14:35.610
But I promise you that

00:14:36.090 --> 00:14:37.420
whatever we have,

00:14:37.610 --> 00:14:38.610
she'll have too.

00:14:40.020 --> 00:14:40.810
Mrs. Lin,

00:14:41.380 --> 00:14:42.210
you can't judge

00:14:42.210 --> 00:14:43.970
just by how things look right now.

00:14:43.970 --> 00:14:45.690
That really would be shortsighted.

00:14:45.730 --> 00:14:47.330
Life is long.

00:14:47.970 --> 00:14:49.900
We have to think long-term.

00:14:50.380 --> 00:14:52.780
Who truly cares about Lin Mei,

00:14:53.210 --> 00:14:55.420
and who she genuinely wants to be with

00:14:55.420 --> 00:14:56.420
are what matter.

00:14:57.610 --> 00:14:59.780
Mom, Fei Ni's right.

00:15:01.180 --> 00:15:02.210
I love Fei Ting.

00:15:02.730 --> 00:15:03.810
I want to be with him.

00:15:07.210 --> 00:15:08.780
I hope you'll support me.

00:15:13.610 --> 00:15:15.210
Let's say, hypothetically,

00:15:15.610 --> 00:15:16.970
you do get married.

00:15:17.493 --> 00:15:18.300
Where will you live?

00:15:18.780 --> 00:15:19.900
And another thing,

00:15:20.300 --> 00:15:22.450
when will your job be settled?

00:15:23.540 --> 00:15:25.330
Mr. Lin, Mrs. Lin, here's the plan.

00:15:25.330 --> 00:15:26.400
After we marry, we'll live

00:15:26.400 --> 00:15:27.540
with my family in the factory

00:15:27.770 --> 00:15:28.880
housing compound.

00:15:29.250 --> 00:15:30.970
We'll have our own room.

00:15:30.970 --> 00:15:34.100
It's an apartment with washrooms
and toilets on each floor.

00:15:34.360 --> 00:15:35.180
As for work,

00:15:36.071 --> 00:15:37.537
I'll settle it as soon as possible.

00:15:40.940 --> 00:15:42.960
Then we'll talk after you've settled it.

00:15:43.210 --> 00:15:45.890
Fei Ni can talk all she wants,

00:15:46.140 --> 00:15:46.670
but

00:15:46.670 --> 00:15:49.020
no matter how beautifully you phrase it,

00:15:49.410 --> 00:15:50.500
I will not marry my daughter

00:15:50.500 --> 00:15:51.810
to an unemployed man.

00:15:52.493 --> 00:15:53.540
That's my bottom line.

00:15:54.480 --> 00:15:57.340
Mrs. Lin,
do you mean that once my brother

00:15:57.340 --> 00:15:58.330
has a job,

00:15:58.520 --> 00:15:59.890
you'll agree to the marriage?

00:16:01.200 --> 00:16:04.260
That depends on what kind of job it is.

00:16:09.330 --> 00:16:09.890
All right.

00:16:10.620 --> 00:16:11.210
I understand.

00:16:18.420 --> 00:16:19.680
(When our comrades
face difficulties,)

00:16:19.680 --> 00:16:21.248
(we must see our achievements,
see the light,)

00:16:21.271 --> 00:16:22.180
(and bolster our courage.)

00:16:26.810 --> 00:16:28.340
Dad, you're in a great mood today

00:16:28.570 --> 00:16:29.630
to have a drink with me.

00:16:29.630 --> 00:16:30.380
Let me.

00:16:32.330 --> 00:16:33.490
That's enough.

00:16:34.730 --> 00:16:36.900
Enough.

00:16:36.900 --> 00:16:37.970
That's good, Dad. Thanks.

00:16:39.260 --> 00:16:40.210
I can't hold my liquor.

00:16:41.970 --> 00:16:45.090
Afraid you'll say
something you shouldn't?

00:16:45.210 --> 00:16:46.180
No.

00:16:46.180 --> 00:16:48.420
Ask me anything. I'll tell you.

00:16:49.970 --> 00:16:50.510
Good.

00:16:50.910 --> 00:16:51.280
Cheers.

00:16:58.060 --> 00:16:59.540
Ni told me

00:17:00.260 --> 00:17:01.690
your memory's back.

00:17:02.330 --> 00:17:02.850
Yes.

00:17:03.900 --> 00:17:05.420
That's good. Very good. Cheers.

00:17:07.420 --> 00:17:10.180
You were sent down at seventeen.

00:17:10.880 --> 00:17:11.620
Yes.

00:17:19.770 --> 00:17:22.010
Stayed in Great Northern Wilderness
the whole time?

00:17:22.380 --> 00:17:23.530
Never transferred?

00:17:23.530 --> 00:17:24.940
Tell me about it.

00:17:25.290 --> 00:17:26.290
What was it like there?

00:17:26.970 --> 00:17:28.140
There's a lot to tell.

00:17:30.860 --> 00:17:31.530
Good, good.

00:17:31.530 --> 00:17:32.290
Come on,

00:17:32.290 --> 00:17:33.340
bottoms up.

00:17:43.380 --> 00:17:44.770
Start from the beginning.

00:17:44.770 --> 00:17:46.380
That first year

00:17:46.490 --> 00:17:48.250
at the Great Northern Wilderness
youth post,

00:17:48.340 --> 00:17:49.820
how many were there?

00:17:50.140 --> 00:17:51.010
How many men?

00:17:51.340 --> 00:17:52.290
How many women?

00:17:52.690 --> 00:17:53.620
The first year,

00:17:54.010 --> 00:17:56.210
we had eighteen in total.

00:17:56.210 --> 00:17:57.290
Twelve men,

00:17:57.970 --> 00:17:58.940
six women.

00:17:59.210 --> 00:18:00.420
What about the second year?

00:18:02.420 --> 00:18:03.970
A lot came in the second year.

00:18:04.340 --> 00:18:06.450
From Henan, Hebei,

00:18:06.710 --> 00:18:07.740
Shanxi, Shandong,

00:18:08.690 --> 00:18:11.940
Jiangsu, and Sichuan.

00:18:13.180 --> 00:18:14.530
How many from Hebei?

00:18:14.730 --> 00:18:17.420
Two men, four women.

00:18:18.620 --> 00:18:19.420
Shanxi?

00:18:19.770 --> 00:18:23.380
Six men, two women.

00:18:23.860 --> 00:18:24.530
Jiangsu?

00:18:24.530 --> 00:18:25.290
Jiangsu...

00:18:28.970 --> 00:18:29.770
Hubei.

00:18:30.620 --> 00:18:34.010
That's where your mother
and I got married.

00:18:36.100 --> 00:18:37.140
Did you know that?

00:18:37.770 --> 00:18:40.420
Back then, I was just

00:18:40.710 --> 00:18:42.450
a farm boy.

00:18:43.610 --> 00:18:45.490
The county's Peking Opera troupe

00:18:45.490 --> 00:18:47.260
came to the village scouting talent.

00:18:47.620 --> 00:18:50.210
Most people didn't dare go.

00:18:50.210 --> 00:18:51.530
They were afraid

00:18:51.860 --> 00:18:53.450
they'd lose their farmland.

00:18:53.870 --> 00:18:55.140
But not me.

00:18:55.680 --> 00:18:57.290
Your old man

00:18:57.580 --> 00:18:58.620
got good looks.

00:19:00.640 --> 00:19:02.750
I threw in a backflip,

00:19:03.250 --> 00:19:05.340
and they took me on the spot.

00:19:05.730 --> 00:19:09.620
The next year, the young
actresses in the troupe,

00:19:09.620 --> 00:19:11.620
at least eight or ten of them,

00:19:11.620 --> 00:19:13.010
had their eyes on me.

00:19:13.071 --> 00:19:15.970
The young lady, Xu Guihua, was a huadan.
[* A young female role in Peking Opera.]

00:19:16.820 --> 00:19:20.420
She was dressed in a green robe,
still dancing on stage.

00:19:20.420 --> 00:19:21.380
Luo Yufen.

00:19:24.140 --> 00:19:25.250
And there was also

00:19:25.450 --> 00:19:26.290
that...

00:19:26.860 --> 00:19:28.620
That pretty arts soldier.

00:19:28.940 --> 00:19:31.290
I think the surname was Lin.

00:19:32.290 --> 00:19:36.250
Well, a big forest
has all kinds of birds.

00:19:36.620 --> 00:19:37.970
Come on, another drink.

00:19:38.210 --> 00:19:40.290
Give it here, lightweight drinker.

00:19:42.690 --> 00:19:47.970
Tonight we drink
to celebrate our victory.

00:19:48.860 --> 00:19:49.450
Easy, easy.

00:19:49.450 --> 00:19:55.820
Until our ambitions are fulfilled,
we won't rest!

00:19:55.970 --> 00:19:57.770
We'll prove ourselves yet...

00:19:57.770 --> 00:19:58.380
Dad...

00:19:58.380 --> 00:19:59.090
Slow down.

00:20:00.190 --> 00:20:00.690
Careful.

00:20:00.690 --> 00:20:03.140
- We'll gladly shed our burning blood!
- Dad!

00:20:07.690 --> 00:20:09.530
I can't walk anymore.

00:20:09.690 --> 00:20:11.770
Let me lie down here for a bit.

00:20:12.210 --> 00:20:13.420
You head back first.

00:20:13.820 --> 00:20:15.580
I'll go home when I wake up.

00:20:17.820 --> 00:20:18.700
I'll stay with you.

00:20:26.210 --> 00:20:29.520
Fang, tell me the truth.

00:20:30.760 --> 00:20:32.250
In Great Northern Wilderness,

00:20:33.420 --> 00:20:34.940
were you ever married?

00:20:36.180 --> 00:20:38.010
Do you have a child?

00:20:39.380 --> 00:20:40.210
Dad,

00:20:40.770 --> 00:20:41.900
I promise you,

00:20:41.937 --> 00:20:43.448
back in Great Northern Wilderness,

00:20:43.530 --> 00:20:44.580
I was never married,

00:20:44.960 --> 00:20:46.010
and I have no children.

00:20:46.490 --> 00:20:47.690
Don't lie to me.

00:20:47.690 --> 00:20:48.860
You can't lie.

00:20:48.860 --> 00:20:49.620
I'm not.

00:20:51.730 --> 00:20:53.490
I promise you and Mom that

00:20:54.770 --> 00:20:55.730
Fei Ni

00:20:56.290 --> 00:20:57.820
is the only woman I'll ever love.

00:21:04.210 --> 00:21:05.730
Good.

00:21:07.290 --> 00:21:08.130
Fang.

00:21:08.450 --> 00:21:10.810
You are fortunate

00:21:11.180 --> 00:21:13.010
to have married Fei Ni.

00:21:13.340 --> 00:21:14.100
Understand?

00:21:14.900 --> 00:21:15.420
Yes.

00:21:15.730 --> 00:21:17.250
My daughter

00:21:17.730 --> 00:21:18.770
is very talented,

00:21:18.970 --> 00:21:19.940
beautiful,

00:21:21.010 --> 00:21:21.770
and kind.

00:21:24.210 --> 00:21:26.050
Such a wonderful girl.

00:21:32.140 --> 00:21:34.620
It's just that her father's no good.

00:21:35.420 --> 00:21:37.820
When other girls get married,

00:21:38.020 --> 00:21:39.730
they get the Four Big Items.

00:21:40.310 --> 00:21:41.770
The full set of furniture.

00:21:42.730 --> 00:21:43.970
And our Ni?

00:21:44.970 --> 00:21:46.100
Her new home

00:21:46.100 --> 00:21:48.270
barely has anything.

00:21:49.140 --> 00:21:51.530
Forget a proper wedding.

00:21:52.340 --> 00:21:54.180
I couldn't even

00:21:55.210 --> 00:21:56.580
put out some wedding candy.

00:21:59.490 --> 00:22:00.290
I know

00:22:02.100 --> 00:22:04.530
our Ni is sensible.

00:22:05.140 --> 00:22:07.140
She knows we don't have money.

00:22:07.140 --> 00:22:08.820
She didn't want us to spend it.

00:22:09.900 --> 00:22:11.770
But that's because her father

00:22:12.190 --> 00:22:14.010
isn't capable.

00:22:15.340 --> 00:22:16.530
Tell me,

00:22:16.660 --> 00:22:19.210
what kind of father am I?

00:22:20.940 --> 00:22:22.380
When it came to college,

00:22:22.380 --> 00:22:24.970
I couldn't help her much.

00:22:25.530 --> 00:22:28.380
When it came to housing,
I couldn't help either.

00:22:28.900 --> 00:22:31.180
I feel sorry for her!

00:22:36.690 --> 00:22:37.490
Dad,

00:22:38.940 --> 00:22:40.180
Fei Ni is lucky

00:22:40.180 --> 00:22:41.450
to be born into this family.

00:22:45.050 --> 00:22:46.420
You all love her so much.

00:22:47.290 --> 00:22:49.010
Can love put food on the table?

00:22:49.010 --> 00:22:49.830
Let me tell you,

00:22:49.830 --> 00:22:51.940
sometimes I regret it.

00:22:52.530 --> 00:22:54.000
If I had married

00:22:54.000 --> 00:22:56.190
Luo Yufen instead,

00:22:56.700 --> 00:22:58.850
would I be living like this now?

00:22:59.250 --> 00:23:00.770
Luo Yufen is now

00:23:00.770 --> 00:23:02.940
a leader in the cultural bureau.

00:23:03.690 --> 00:23:06.720
No, if I'd married Luo Yufen,

00:23:07.620 --> 00:23:09.480
there wouldn't be our Ni.

00:23:10.340 --> 00:23:11.940
No Fei Ting either.

00:23:11.940 --> 00:23:14.100
Not even Comrade Wu Baoying.

00:23:14.180 --> 00:23:14.940
No!

00:23:14.940 --> 00:23:16.690
I couldn't give them up.

00:23:17.010 --> 00:23:19.620
I want Fei Ting. I want Fei Ni.

00:23:19.620 --> 00:23:20.900
I want Wu Baoying.

00:23:22.620 --> 00:23:24.580
More booze...

00:23:43.010 --> 00:23:43.530
Fei.

00:23:45.900 --> 00:23:46.770
Wake up.

00:23:46.970 --> 00:23:48.530
Fang, let's drink.

00:23:48.770 --> 00:23:49.970
Still drinking?

00:23:50.690 --> 00:23:52.010
Fang?

00:23:52.290 --> 00:23:54.440
You were lying
on his lap for four hours.

00:23:54.440 --> 00:23:55.200
Do you know that?

00:23:55.900 --> 00:23:57.360
Fei Ting searched everywhere for you

00:23:57.360 --> 00:23:58.530
before carrying you home.

00:24:00.010 --> 00:24:00.720
Fei Ting!

00:24:01.290 --> 00:24:02.940
My son's back.

00:24:04.380 --> 00:24:04.980
Well?

00:24:07.730 --> 00:24:09.140
How did the proposal go?

00:24:10.140 --> 00:24:11.580
Pretty smoothly.

00:24:12.340 --> 00:24:14.690
Mom said you were going
to get Fang Muyang drunk.

00:24:15.010 --> 00:24:16.420
How did you end up drunk instead?

00:24:16.940 --> 00:24:18.770
You clearly don't understand drinking.

00:24:19.620 --> 00:24:21.080
If I didn't get drunk,

00:24:21.350 --> 00:24:22.900
how was I supposed to get him drunk?

00:24:23.290 --> 00:24:24.340
That's called,

00:24:24.340 --> 00:24:29.620
"Nothing ventured, nothing gained."

00:24:29.620 --> 00:24:30.690
Where's my shoe?

00:24:32.900 --> 00:24:34.180
Why is one missing?

00:24:34.180 --> 00:24:35.380
Where's my shoe?

00:24:36.690 --> 00:24:37.580
Go look for it.

00:24:37.580 --> 00:24:38.420
My shoe!

00:24:38.420 --> 00:24:39.620
Where'd it go?

00:24:39.620 --> 00:24:40.380
Oh no, Dad.

00:24:40.660 --> 00:24:43.420
It might have fallen off
when I carried you back.

00:24:43.770 --> 00:24:45.140
Go find it!

00:24:45.140 --> 00:24:46.290
Look carefully!

00:24:48.071 --> 00:24:49.180
Can't you do anything right?

00:24:49.180 --> 00:24:50.210
Anything at all?

00:24:51.770 --> 00:24:52.940
So you "ventured" with him,

00:24:53.004 --> 00:24:54.010
where's the result?

00:24:54.380 --> 00:24:55.620
What did you find out?

00:24:57.420 --> 00:24:58.340
Fang

00:24:58.860 --> 00:24:59.820
is a good kid.

00:25:04.620 --> 00:25:05.010
That's it?

00:25:05.380 --> 00:25:06.100
Yep.

00:25:06.970 --> 00:25:07.900
Fei Mingde!

00:25:08.290 --> 00:25:09.100
After eight hours

00:25:09.100 --> 00:25:09.940
and all that liquor,

00:25:09.940 --> 00:25:11.140
and that's all you got?

00:25:12.210 --> 00:25:14.580
What more do you want to hear?

00:25:15.490 --> 00:25:17.820
No news is the best news.

00:25:17.820 --> 00:25:19.290
Would you rather I tell you

00:25:19.290 --> 00:25:21.490
he's got a wife
in Great Northern Wilderness

00:25:21.490 --> 00:25:22.770
and two illegitimate kids?

00:25:23.010 --> 00:25:24.140
Would that make you happy?

00:25:27.530 --> 00:25:28.500
Honey.

00:25:28.760 --> 00:25:29.450
You stink.

00:25:29.450 --> 00:25:30.380
Go wash up.

00:25:31.620 --> 00:25:34.210
I only drank, didn't eat a thing.

00:25:34.290 --> 00:25:35.210
What's left at home?

00:25:35.210 --> 00:25:36.340
Make me a bite.

00:25:36.340 --> 00:25:37.490
All you think about is food.

00:26:24.970 --> 00:26:25.530
Dad.

00:26:26.210 --> 00:26:27.420
Xu Guihua,

00:26:28.390 --> 00:26:29.660
Luo Yufen,

00:26:30.340 --> 00:26:31.230
and that arts soldier

00:26:31.230 --> 00:26:32.620
you once knew,

00:26:32.620 --> 00:26:33.420
Ms. Lin...

00:26:34.182 --> 00:26:35.220
(Behind the photo frame)

00:26:35.220 --> 00:26:36.380
(are two liquor coupons)

00:26:36.520 --> 00:26:37.450
(and 8.5 yuan.)

00:26:37.826 --> 00:26:39.600
(Plus the meat coupon
you lost last month.)

00:26:39.900 --> 00:26:40.830
(I remember everything.)

00:26:41.180 --> 00:26:42.810
(We're on the same boat now.)

00:26:43.040 --> 00:26:44.870
(Put in a good word
for me with Mom.)

00:26:47.860 --> 00:26:49.040
Why did I blurt all that out?

00:26:54.620 --> 00:26:55.490
Still numb?

00:26:56.140 --> 00:26:56.660
Yeah.

00:26:57.490 --> 00:26:58.380
Can't feel it.

00:26:58.940 --> 00:27:00.820
You couldn't move his head?

00:27:01.450 --> 00:27:02.580
The ground was hard.

00:27:02.820 --> 00:27:03.940
How much did you two drink?

00:27:05.380 --> 00:27:06.770
More than 500 mL.

00:27:07.582 --> 00:27:09.093
Your dad had at least 450 mL.

00:27:09.770 --> 00:27:11.100
That much?

00:27:11.180 --> 00:27:11.810
Yeah.

00:27:13.140 --> 00:27:14.610
He told me every embarrassing thing

00:27:14.610 --> 00:27:15.620
you've done as a kid.

00:27:16.730 --> 00:27:17.770
What did he say?

00:27:18.380 --> 00:27:19.420
He said...

00:27:22.010 --> 00:27:23.530
He and your mom love you very much.

00:27:27.210 --> 00:27:28.730
Do you know how much I envy you?

00:27:29.620 --> 00:27:31.530
Envy me for what?

00:27:32.048 --> 00:27:34.020
For having a family
that loves you like this.

00:27:35.730 --> 00:27:37.010
Your mom may nag,

00:27:37.470 --> 00:27:39.820
but when it comes to you,
she worries the most.

00:27:40.620 --> 00:27:41.900
Your dad may seem unreliable,

00:27:42.870 --> 00:27:44.620
but once he's drunk,
all he talks about

00:27:44.900 --> 00:27:45.530
is you.

00:27:47.380 --> 00:27:48.490
And your brother too.

00:27:49.770 --> 00:27:51.180
I think I finally understand

00:27:52.690 --> 00:27:54.510
why I feel so at ease when I'm with you.

00:27:57.620 --> 00:27:58.800
You grew up

00:27:59.690 --> 00:28:01.090
showered with your family's love.

00:28:04.490 --> 00:28:05.420
I benefit from that too.

00:28:12.730 --> 00:28:13.180
Fei Ni,

00:28:15.820 --> 00:28:17.730
what's your dream wedding like?

00:28:21.290 --> 00:28:22.420
I've never thought about it.

00:28:22.970 --> 00:28:23.900
Then think about it now.

00:28:28.860 --> 00:28:30.180
Maybe...

00:28:31.210 --> 00:28:33.580
with my dad, my mom,
and my brother all there.

00:28:34.620 --> 00:28:37.290
We'll have it lively and warm.

00:30:30.690 --> 00:30:32.140
Why are you back so late?

00:30:34.900 --> 00:30:35.690
Sketching.

00:30:36.860 --> 00:30:38.620
You can sketch this late?

00:30:42.160 --> 00:30:43.490
Observing nocturnal animals.

00:30:44.250 --> 00:30:45.050
By the way, Fei Ni,

00:30:45.450 --> 00:30:46.560
can you knit a mesh bag?

00:30:47.350 --> 00:30:48.050
Sure.

00:30:48.450 --> 00:30:50.340
We're doing
still-life sketching next lesson.

00:30:50.360 --> 00:30:52.100
The perspective through a mesh is great.

00:30:52.490 --> 00:30:53.620
Can you make me one?

00:30:53.940 --> 00:30:54.900
The bigger the better.

00:30:55.860 --> 00:30:56.660
No problem.

00:30:58.420 --> 00:30:58.820
All right.

00:31:00.140 --> 00:31:01.420
I'll wash up.

00:31:09.900 --> 00:31:10.860
You're going out?

00:31:11.820 --> 00:31:12.930
To Jiangcheng.

00:31:13.920 --> 00:31:14.550
On business?

00:31:15.900 --> 00:31:17.340
My younger brother wrote.

00:31:17.660 --> 00:31:19.340
He invited me to his wedding.

00:31:21.737 --> 00:31:23.120
Do you want me to go with you?

00:31:25.900 --> 00:31:26.860
Do you want to?

00:31:28.900 --> 00:31:30.730
If you want me there, I'll go.

00:31:33.290 --> 00:31:34.290
Then don't.

00:31:35.660 --> 00:31:37.530
My brother's always been carefree,

00:31:37.690 --> 00:31:38.690
full of tricks.

00:31:39.140 --> 00:31:40.210
You wouldn't like him.

00:31:41.900 --> 00:31:43.340
At least in my opinion,

00:31:43.340 --> 00:31:44.626
he has one redeeming quality.

00:31:44.690 --> 00:31:45.490
What's that?

00:31:46.900 --> 00:31:47.690
He has a heart.

00:31:49.050 --> 00:31:50.490
At the very least,

00:31:50.490 --> 00:31:51.490
he invited you.

00:31:52.630 --> 00:31:53.860
So you're implying

00:31:54.900 --> 00:31:55.730
I don't have a heart?

00:31:56.140 --> 00:31:57.250
I didn't say that.

00:31:57.626 --> 00:32:00.093
If that's how you choose to take it,
I can't help that.

00:32:01.450 --> 00:32:02.530
Finish packing.

00:32:02.530 --> 00:32:03.530
I'm going to shower.

00:32:11.810 --> 00:32:12.970
All aboard!

00:32:13.120 --> 00:32:14.670
(Jiangnan)
The train to Jiangcheng

00:32:14.670 --> 00:32:15.830
is about to depart.

00:32:16.100 --> 00:32:17.450
Please get on quickly!

00:32:33.010 --> 00:32:33.820
Sorry, Comrade.

00:32:34.010 --> 00:32:34.730
It's fine.

00:33:25.730 --> 00:33:26.390
Sorry.

00:33:31.660 --> 00:33:32.730
What are you doing here?

00:33:33.620 --> 00:33:36.090
The person sitting here
got off at Yongxing.

00:33:37.620 --> 00:33:38.860
I've been here fifteen minutes.

00:33:39.140 --> 00:33:40.530
You didn't look up once.

00:33:41.340 --> 00:33:44.210
You're probably the most focused reader

00:33:44.620 --> 00:33:45.860
I've ever met.

00:33:46.420 --> 00:33:47.690
But I should mention that

00:33:47.860 --> 00:33:49.210
looking down at a book for too long

00:33:49.580 --> 00:33:50.620
isn't good

00:33:50.620 --> 00:33:51.420
for your neck.

00:33:53.620 --> 00:33:54.871
Liu, play a few hands for me.

00:33:54.915 --> 00:33:55.970
I'm going to the restroom.

00:33:55.970 --> 00:33:56.380
Okay.

00:34:03.900 --> 00:34:05.050
Where are you headed?

00:34:05.250 --> 00:34:06.050
Jiangcheng.

00:34:09.490 --> 00:34:10.490
Don't misunderstand.

00:34:10.493 --> 00:34:11.700
It has nothing to do with you.

00:34:13.300 --> 00:34:15.450
The hospital assigned me to Jiangcheng

00:34:15.450 --> 00:34:18.090
for a neurosurgery symposium.

00:34:21.450 --> 00:34:22.260
What a coincidence.

00:34:23.450 --> 00:34:23.900
Yes.

00:34:24.780 --> 00:34:25.860
Quite a coincidence.

00:34:29.960 --> 00:34:30.610
By the way...

00:34:32.610 --> 00:34:34.340
I happened to buy two sleeper tickets.

00:34:34.960 --> 00:34:36.900
(Hard sleeper)
Why don't you switch to a sleeper?

00:34:36.900 --> 00:34:38.115
If you get tired from reading,

00:34:38.420 --> 00:34:39.860
you can lie down and rest.

00:34:53.980 --> 00:34:56.860
(Hard sleeper ticket)

00:35:00.100 --> 00:35:06.420
(China Science)

00:35:27.782 --> 00:35:29.180
(Introduction to Higher Mathematics)

00:35:40.940 --> 00:35:42.740
If you want to attend
Fang Muyang's wedding,

00:35:43.130 --> 00:35:44.450
I can take you with me.

00:35:46.700 --> 00:35:47.860
I'm not interested.

00:35:48.420 --> 00:35:49.450
Don't misunderstand.

00:35:49.610 --> 00:35:50.940
I didn't come to Jiangcheng

00:35:50.940 --> 00:35:52.050
because of you.

00:35:52.490 --> 00:35:53.490
I told you,

00:35:53.820 --> 00:35:55.300
I'm here on business.

00:35:55.700 --> 00:35:57.010
Of course I don't misunderstand.

00:35:58.130 --> 00:35:59.130
It just so happens

00:35:59.130 --> 00:36:01.300
your hospital sent you to Jiangcheng,

00:36:01.860 --> 00:36:03.940
you happened to book
the same train as me,

00:36:04.260 --> 00:36:06.300
and happened to run into me on board.

00:36:06.900 --> 00:36:08.340
Pure coincidence.

00:36:12.130 --> 00:36:14.340
I'm glad you see it that way.

00:36:14.860 --> 00:36:16.490
Once we reach Jiangcheng,

00:36:16.490 --> 00:36:17.582
we'll mind our own business.

00:36:18.490 --> 00:36:19.340
Sure.

00:37:04.010 --> 00:37:04.780
Comrade,

00:37:04.826 --> 00:37:06.900
could you not spit
sunflower shells everywhere?

00:37:07.130 --> 00:37:07.820
What?

00:37:08.340 --> 00:37:09.050
Did it hit you?

00:37:19.940 --> 00:37:21.490
Please put your feet down.

00:37:21.740 --> 00:37:24.220
My legs are this long.
I need the leg room.

00:37:35.700 --> 00:37:36.490
I'm a doctor.

00:37:36.490 --> 00:37:37.870
I can arrange an amputation.

00:37:38.360 --> 00:37:39.220
What's your problem?

00:37:39.900 --> 00:37:41.610
If you can't crack seeds properly,

00:37:41.610 --> 00:37:43.050
I'll stitch your mouth shut.

00:37:44.700 --> 00:37:45.700
Who are you?

00:37:46.010 --> 00:37:46.820
What's it to you?

00:37:52.740 --> 00:37:53.820
I'm her husband.

00:37:54.010 --> 00:37:55.260
Does that give me the right?

00:37:55.260 --> 00:37:56.180
(Marriage Certificate)

00:38:04.490 --> 00:38:05.450
If I put my feet down,

00:38:05.450 --> 00:38:06.220
would you like it?

00:38:06.280 --> 00:38:08.400
What's wrong with you?
Have some manners.

00:38:10.340 --> 00:38:11.130
Fine.

00:38:11.650 --> 00:38:12.450
I'll stop eating.

00:38:13.340 --> 00:38:14.420
Happy now?

00:38:30.090 --> 00:38:30.900
Take my berth.

00:39:49.782 --> 00:39:50.640
What are you doing?

00:39:51.048 --> 00:39:52.048
What's going on here?

00:39:52.650 --> 00:39:53.740
Comrade!

00:39:54.915 --> 00:39:56.310
Are you sneaking around fishing?

00:39:57.490 --> 00:39:58.780
No, no.

00:39:58.780 --> 00:40:00.090
I was...

00:40:00.090 --> 00:40:01.130
I was picking up trash.

00:40:01.337 --> 00:40:02.982
There's so much litter on the bank.

00:40:06.490 --> 00:40:07.940
You've got good awareness, young man.

00:40:08.450 --> 00:40:09.740
All right, it's pitch dark.

00:40:09.900 --> 00:40:10.610
Head back early.

00:40:10.940 --> 00:40:11.450
Yes.

00:40:11.693 --> 00:40:13.340
Don't forget to take the trash with you.

00:40:13.600 --> 00:40:14.060
Of course.

00:40:14.490 --> 00:40:15.000
Let's go.

00:40:21.090 --> 00:40:21.940
Move it.

00:40:22.300 --> 00:40:23.650
Coming, coming.

00:40:24.900 --> 00:40:25.490
Hurry up.

00:40:47.820 --> 00:40:50.460
(Ten yuan, One yuan)

00:40:53.700 --> 00:40:55.490
(I took the money without telling her.)

00:40:56.130 --> 00:40:57.380
(Was that too much?)

00:41:07.650 --> 00:41:10.130
(Forget a proper wedding.)

00:41:10.130 --> 00:41:12.010
(I couldn't even)

00:41:12.260 --> 00:41:13.530
(put out some wedding candy.)

00:41:14.450 --> 00:41:15.900
(I love this family so much.)

00:41:16.220 --> 00:41:17.700
(So much.)

00:41:18.300 --> 00:41:19.740
(Maybe...)

00:41:19.740 --> 00:41:22.220
(with my dad, my mom,
and my brother all there.)

00:41:22.700 --> 00:41:23.740
(We'll have it)

00:41:24.570 --> 00:41:25.420
(lively and warm.)

00:41:25.650 --> 00:41:26.220
(Fei Ni.)

00:41:27.130 --> 00:41:27.780
(I promise)

00:41:28.226 --> 00:41:29.280
(I'll pay you back soon.)

00:41:31.610 --> 00:41:32.420
Fang Muyang.

00:41:34.610 --> 00:41:36.010
What's so secretive?

00:41:36.010 --> 00:41:36.940
Can't we talk at home?

00:41:37.004 --> 00:41:37.610
Brother-in-law.

00:41:38.450 --> 00:41:40.937
Fei Ni told me that back
in Great Northern Wilderness,

00:41:41.048 --> 00:41:41.940
you fed the whole post

00:41:41.940 --> 00:41:43.130
with just one big iron pot.

00:41:43.130 --> 00:41:44.050
Is that true?

00:41:44.220 --> 00:41:45.340
Of course it's true.

00:41:45.490 --> 00:41:46.610
Let me put it this way.

00:41:46.610 --> 00:41:47.300
Whatever flies,

00:41:47.300 --> 00:41:47.900
runs,

00:41:47.900 --> 00:41:49.130
swims, or hops in the grass,

00:41:49.300 --> 00:41:50.340
if it's edible,

00:41:50.340 --> 00:41:51.860
I can stew it in one pot.

00:41:52.010 --> 00:41:53.260
Then, I've found the right man.

00:41:53.940 --> 00:41:55.260
So, Brother-in-law,

00:41:55.450 --> 00:41:57.010
care to help

00:41:57.220 --> 00:41:58.380
with your sister's wedding?

00:41:59.490 --> 00:42:00.340
The wedding?

00:42:03.100 --> 00:42:07.180
(The masses have boundless creativity.)

00:42:11.450 --> 00:42:13.650
(Xiangyang Road)
Bus No. 4 to Worker-Peasant Hospital.

00:42:15.380 --> 00:42:15.970
What about you?

00:42:16.380 --> 00:42:17.340
I'll head east.

00:42:18.970 --> 00:42:20.300
Be careful on the way.

00:42:32.340 --> 00:42:39.220
(Jiangcheng No. 2 Guesthouse)

00:42:50.848 --> 00:42:52.160
What are you doing here?

00:42:54.380 --> 00:42:55.130
What a coincidence.

00:42:58.610 --> 00:43:00.650
The guesthouses
near the hospital are full.

00:43:00.650 --> 00:43:01.420
So...

00:43:05.848 --> 00:43:07.420
It's your brother's wedding tomorrow.

00:43:07.420 --> 00:43:09.780
Shouldn't you prepare
something for him?

00:43:10.170 --> 00:43:10.610
No.

00:43:11.300 --> 00:43:13.010
I don't even plan to tell him I'm here.

00:43:14.050 --> 00:43:14.860
Why?

00:43:28.860 --> 00:43:33.340
♪After the laughter, I think of you♪

00:43:35.900 --> 00:43:40.620
♪After the storm, I think of you♪

00:43:43.140 --> 00:43:49.260
♪In the little courtyard,
there you are dancing♪

00:43:50.260 --> 00:43:54.820
♪That earnest you,
smiling so innocently♪

00:43:57.300 --> 00:44:02.060
♪In spring, I stay by your side♪

00:44:04.500 --> 00:44:08.860
♪When summer comes, I watch over you♪

00:44:11.220 --> 00:44:17.860
♪In the light of dawn, you belong to me♪

00:44:17.860 --> 00:44:27.460
♪At the edge of the world,
I will still hold you tight♪

00:44:28.540 --> 00:44:34.700
♪There is a small place♪

00:44:34.700 --> 00:44:41.500
♪Where they carry big dreams♪

00:44:41.500 --> 00:44:48.860
♪Every lovely face♪

00:44:49.740 --> 00:44:55.900
♪Shines brightly in the heart♪

00:44:56.700 --> 00:45:02.740
♪Even when we collide,
we hold our course♪

00:45:03.940 --> 00:45:09.740
♪Even when we stumble,
we keep our resolve♪

00:45:10.820 --> 00:45:17.100
♪My you, walking toward the distance♪

00:45:17.900 --> 00:45:26.140
♪Please carry our dreams
and let them soar♪